Mainly based on Holotype, unless indicated as paratype. A well-preserved female adult fossil. Body 12 mm long. Forewing and hind wing overlapping almost entirely, but most of veins discernible. Thorax and abdomen preserved, but head poorly preserved. Legs poorly preserved, with only few fragments (Figs 1A, 2A, 2
C-F
).
